text: Karel and I (Karel a já) is a 1942 Czechoslovak comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Jiří Dohnal, Jana Dítětová, Jaroslav Marvan. ==References== ==External links== *Karel and I (Karel a já) at the Internet Movie Database Category:1942 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak comedy films Category:1942 comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black- and-white films
